/**
 * @brief
 * Cimutils used to take pictures and video.
 * File CameraDemo.sh have created in the directory /testsuit/CameraDemo/
 *
 * Feature:
 *
 * i> save as picture formats:
 * BMP - Windows Bitmap
 * JPEG - Joint Photographic Experts Group
 * Raw - CIM RxFiFo Data
 *
 * ii> V4L2-compatible codes
 *
 * iii> FOURCC-compatible pixel formats
 *
 * iv> preview on LCD
 *
 * v> display raw & picture file on LCD
 *
 * Operation method: ./CameraDemo.sh
 *
 * Add this module in the project:
 *
 * device/\<board\>/\<board\>_base.mk:PRODUCT_MODULES += cimutils
 *
 * @author Ingenic
 *
 * @version 1.0.0
 */
Cimutils Description;
